content: Allows me the Peloton experience on my Echelon EX5-S bike ( you to have the Peloton app installed on your Echelon..yes, its possible)

Game changing app for my Echelon bike! I can now use it to participate in Power Zone training rides. It connects automatically with my bike every time I open the app. I can also save the rides to a file and then upload it to my Strava. Also, the app developer is engaged with the community and super responsive to questions, suggestions and requests; he's made a lot of thoughtful decisions with this app. This purchase was totally worth it!
Great app - brilliant support - really impressed
